## Remarks  
 The Properties property returns system properties for a blob. System properties are stored on the service and must be retrieved via a request to the service. System  properties are defined in the <xref:Microsoft.WindowsAzure.Storage.Blob.BlobProperties> class.  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  To retrieve the blob's system properties, call <xref:Microsoft.WindowsAzure.Storage.Blob.CloudBlob.FetchAttributesAsync%2A> before checking the property values. FetchAttributesAsync makes a request against the service to retrieve the most up-to-date values for system properties.  
  
   
  
